                    answer: "Initiation: Cl₂ → 2Cl• (hν). Propagation: Cl• + C₂H₆ → C₂H₅• + HCl; C₂H₅• + Cl₂ → C₂H₅Cl + Cl•. Termination: any two radical combination steps.",
