                    coagulation: "Aluminium sulfate (Al₂(SO₄)₃) hydrolyses to Al(OH)₃ — weak acid equilibria control floc formation",
                    pHAdjustment: "Lime (Ca(OH)₂) used to raise pH; CO₂ used to lower pH"
