                    halfReactionAcidic: "MnO₄⁻ + 8H⁺ + 5e⁻ → Mn²⁺ + 4H₂O  (acidic medium)",
                    halfReactionBasic: "MnO₄⁻ + 2H₂O + 3e⁻ → MnO₂ + 4OH⁻  (basic/neutral medium)",
